      A digital broadsheet dedicated to the preservation of logic and the dissemination of classical wisdom in a modern context.
    </p>
    <p class="font-label uppercase tracking-tighter text-[10px] text-secondary">
      Curated by Tanmay Goel
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h4 class="font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold text-primary">Navigation</h4>
    <ul class="space-y-2 flex flex-col">
      <li><a href="#" class="font-body text-lg text-secondary opacity-80 hover:text-primary transition-all underline decoration-primary decoration-2">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="font-body text-lg text-secondary opacity-80 hover:text-primary transition-all">Terms of Service</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="font-body text-lg text-secondary opacity-80 hover:text-primary transition-all">Contact</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="font-body text-lg text-secondary opacity-80 hover:text-primary transition-all">Back to Top</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h4 class="font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold text-primary">Connect</h4>
    <div class="flex space-x-4">
      <a href="#" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-all underline decoration-1">Twitter</a>
      <a href="#" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-all underline decoration-1">Substack</a>
